{
  "video_id": "CfqO1U6lfDs",
  "title": "Ed Yong: Suicidal wasps, zombie roaches and other parasite tales",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12645.0,
      "end_time": 15196.0,
      "text": "A herd of wildebeests, a shoal of fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15196.0,
      "end_time": 16825.0,
      "text": "a flock of birds."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16825.0,
      "end_time": 18893.0,
      "text": "Many animals gather in large groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18893.0,
      "end_time": 20879.0,
      "text": "that are among the most wonderful spectacles"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20879.0,
      "end_time": 22597.0,
      "text": "in the natural world."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22597.0,
      "end_time": 25321.0,
      "text": "But why do these groups form?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25321.0,
      "end_time": 26958.0,
      "text": "The common answers include things like"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26958.0,
      "end_time": 29924.0,
      "text": "seeking safety in numbers or hunting in packs"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29924.0,
      "end_time": 32420.0,
      "text": "or gathering to mate or breed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32420.0,
      "end_time": 34088.0,
      "text": "and all of these explanations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34088.0,
      "end_time": 35325.0,
      "text": "while often true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35325.0,
      "end_time": 38368.0,
      "text": "make a huge assumption about animal behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38368.0,
      "end_time": 41545.0,
      "text": "that the animals are in control of their own actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41545.0,
      "end_time": 43796.0,
      "text": "that they are in charge of their bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43796.0,
      "end_time": 47223.0,
      "text": "And that is often not the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47223.0,
      "end_time": 50147.0,
      "text": "This is Artemia, a brine shrimp."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50147.0,
      "end_time": 52911.0,
      "text": "You probably know it better as a sea monkey."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52911.0,
      "end_time": 54906.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s small, and it typically lives alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54906.0,
      "end_time": 57983.0,
      "text": "but it can gather in these large red swarms"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57983.0,
      "end_time": 60230.0,
      "text": "that span for meters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60230.0,
      "end_time": 63320.0,
      "text": "and these form because of a parasite."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63320.0,
      "end_time": 66006.0,
      "text": "These shrimp are infected with a tapeworm."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66006.0,
      "end_time": 68257.0,
      "text": "A tapeworm is effectively a long, living gut"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68257.0,
      "end_time": 71145.0,
      "text": "with genitals at one end and a hooked mouth at the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71145.0,
      "end_time": 73680.0,
      "text": "As a freelance journalist, I sympathize."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73680.0,
      "end_time": 75835.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75835.0,
      "end_time": 78743.0,
      "text": "The tapeworm drains nutrients from Artemia&#39;s body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78743.0,
      "end_time": 80820.0,
      "text": "but it also does other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80820.0,
      "end_time": 82440.0,
      "text": "It castrates them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82440.0,
      "end_time": 87158.0,
      "text": "it changes their color from transparent to bright red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87158.0,
      "end_time": 88674.0,
      "text": "it makes them live longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88674.0,
      "end_time": 91031.0,
      "text": "and as biologist Nicolas Rode has found,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91031.0,
      "end_time": 94390.0,
      "text": "it makes them swim in groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94390.0,
      "end_time": 97842.0,
      "text": "Why? Because the tapeworm, like many other parasites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97842.0,
      "end_time": 99423.0,
      "text": "has a complicated life cycle"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99423.0,
      "end_time": 101687.0,
      "text": "involving many different hosts."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101687.0,
      "end_time": 104091.0,
      "text": "The shrimp are just one step on its journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104091.0,
      "end_time": 106703.0,
      "text": "Its ultimate destination is this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106703.0,
      "end_time": 108650.0,
      "text": "the greater flamingo."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108650.0,
      "end_time": 111675.0,
      "text": "Only in a flamingo can the tapeworm reproduce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111675.0,
      "end_time": 114964.0,
      "text": "so to get there, it manipulates its shrimp hosts"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114964.0,
      "end_time": 118055.0,
      "text": "into forming these conspicuous colored swarms"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118055.0,
      "end_time": 120772.0,
      "text": "that are easier for a flamingo to spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120772.0,
      "end_time": 122331.0,
      "text": "and to devour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122331.0,
      "end_time": 125263.0,
      "text": "and that is the secret of the Artemia swarm."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125263.0,
      "end_time": 127426.0,
      "text": "They aren&#39;t sociable through their own volition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127426.0,
      "end_time": 129502.0,
      "text": "but because they are being controlled."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129502.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131196.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not safety in numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131196.0,
      "end_time": 133055.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually the exact opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 133055.0,
      "end_time": 136096.0,
      "text": "The tapeworm hijacks their brains and their bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136096.0,
      "end_time": 137492.0,
      "text": "turning them into vehicles"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 137492.0,
      "end_time": 141459.0,
      "text": "for getting itself into a flamingo."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141459.0,
      "end_time": 142889.0,
      "text": "And here is another example"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 142889.0,
      "end_time": 145415.0,
      "text": "of a parasitic manipulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145415.0,
      "end_time": 148391.0,
      "text": "This is a suicidal cricket."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148391.0,
      "end_time": 151695.0,
      "text": "This cricket swallowed the larvae of a Gordian worm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 151695.0,
      "end_time": 153588.0,
      "text": "or horsehair worm."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153588.0,
      "end_time": 155744.0,
      "text": "The worm grew to adult size within it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155744.0,
      "end_time": 158782.0,
      "text": "but it needs to get into water in order to mate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 158782.0,
      "end_time": 161000.0,
      "text": "and it does that by releasing proteins"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161000.0,
      "end_time": 163188.0,
      "text": "that addle the cricket&#39;s brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 163188.0,
      "end_time": 165352.0,
      "text": "causing it to behave erratically."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165352.0,
      "end_time": 167307.0,
      "text": "When the cricket nears a body of water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 167307.0,
      "end_time": 168926.0,
      "text": "such as this swimming pool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168926.0,
      "end_time": 171183.0,
      "text": "it jumps in and drowns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171183.0,
      "end_time": 172908.0,
      "text": "and the worm wriggles out"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172908.0,
      "end_time": 176764.0,
      "text": "of its suicidal corpse."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176764.0,
      "end_time": 180367.0,
      "text": "Crickets are really roomy. Who knew?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 180367.0,
      "end_time": 183582.0,
      "text": "The tapeworm and the Gordian worm are not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 183582.0,
      "end_time": 185302.0,
      "text": "They are part of an entire cavalcade"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185302.0,
      "end_time": 187379.0,
      "text": "of mind-controlling parasites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187379.0,
      "end_time": 191328.0,
      "text": "of fungi, viruses, and worms and insects and more"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 191328.0,
      "end_time": 193901.0,
      "text": "that all specialize in subverting and overriding"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 193901.0,
      "end_time": 196110.0,
      "text": "the wills of their hosts."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196110.0,
      "end_time": 197847.0,
      "text": "Now, I first learned about this way of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 197847.0,
      "end_time": 200340.0,
      "text": "through David Attenborough&#39;s &quot;Trials of Life&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 200340.0,
      "end_time": 202062.0,
      "text": "about 20 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 202062.0,
      "end_time": 203764.0,
      "text": "and then later through a wonderful book called"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 203764.0,
      "end_time": 206438.0,
      "text": "&quot;Parasite Rex&quot; by my friend Carl Zimmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 206438.0,
      "end_time": 208581.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve been writing about these creatures ever since."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 208581.0,
      "end_time": 211392.0,
      "text": "Few topics in biology enthrall me more."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 211392.0,
      "end_time": 215098.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like the parasites have subverted my own brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 215098.0,
      "end_time": 217709.0,
      "text": "Because after all, they are always compelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 217709.0,
      "end_time": 218997.0,
      "text": "and they are delightfully macabre."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 218997.0,
      "end_time": 220389.0,
      "text": "When you write about parasites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 220389.0,
      "end_time": 222473.0,
      "text": "your lexicon swells with phrases like"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 222473.0,
      "end_time": 225519.0,
      "text": "&quot;devoured alive&quot; and &quot;bursts out of its body.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 225519.0,
      "end_time": 226756.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 226756.0,
      "end_time": 228296.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s more to it than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 228296.0,
      "end_time": 230398.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a writer, and fellow writers in the audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 230398.0,
      "end_time": 233107.0,
      "text": "will know that we love stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 233107.0,
      "end_time": 235500.0,
      "text": "Parasites invite us to resist the allure"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 235500.0,
      "end_time": 237350.0,
      "text": "of obvious stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 237350.0,
      "end_time": 239660.0,
      "text": "Their world is one of plot twists"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 239660.0,
      "end_time": 243267.0,
      "text": "and unexpected explanations."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 243267.0,
      "end_time": 244763.0,
      "text": "Why, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 244763.0,
      "end_time": 246941.0,
      "text": "does this caterpillar"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 246941.0,
      "end_time": 248915.0,
      "text": "start violently thrashing about"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 248915.0,
      "end_time": 250583.0,
      "text": "when another insect gets close to it"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 250583.0,
      "end_time": 252840.0,
      "text": "and those white cocoons that it seems"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 252840.0,
      "end_time": 254278.0,
      "text": "to be standing guard over?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254278.0,
      "end_time": 257374.0,
      "text": "Is it maybe protecting its siblings?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 257374.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258823.00000000003,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 258822.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260279.99999999997,
      "text": "This caterpillar was attacked"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 260279.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263499.0,
      "text": "by a parasitic wasp which laid eggs inside it."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 263499.0,
      "end_time": 264933.0,
      "text": "The eggs hatched and the young wasps"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 264933.0,
      "end_time": 266247.0,
      "text": "devoured the caterpillar alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 266247.0,
      "end_time": 267918.0,
      "text": "before bursting out of its body."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 267918.0,
      "end_time": 270193.0,
      "text": "See what I mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 270193.0,
      "end_time": 273031.0,
      "text": "Now, the caterpillar didn&#39;t die."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 273031.0,
      "end_time": 275616.0,
      "text": "Some of the wasps seemed to stay behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 275616.0,
      "end_time": 278953.0,
      "text": "and controlled it into defending their siblings"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 278953.0,
      "end_time": 280587.0,
      "text": "which are metamorphosing"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 280587.0,
      "end_time": 282607.0,
      "text": "into adults within those cocoons."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282607.0,
      "end_time": 286146.0,
      "text": "This caterpillar is a head-banging zombie bodyguard"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 286146.0,
      "end_time": 287447.0,
      "text": "defending the offspring"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 287447.0,
      "end_time": 289669.0,
      "text": "of the creature that killed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 289669.0,
      "end_time": 293535.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 293535.0,
      "end_time": 297830.0,
      "text": "We have a lot to get through. I only have 13 minutes. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 297830.0,
      "end_time": 299641.0,
      "text": "Now, some of you are probably just"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 299641.0,
      "end_time": 301859.0,
      "text": "desperately clawing for some solace"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 301859.0,
      "end_time": 304119.0,
      "text": "in the idea that these things are oddities"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 304119.0,
      "end_time": 306050.0,
      "text": "of the natural world, that they are outliers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 306050.0,
      "end_time": 307870.0,
      "text": "and that point of view is understandable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 307870.0,
      "end_time": 310248.0,
      "text": "because by their nature, parasites are quite small"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 310248.0,
      "end_time": 311588.0,
      "text": "and they spend a lot of their time"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 311588.0,
      "end_time": 314542.0,
      "text": "inside the bodies of other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 314542.0,
      "end_time": 316313.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re easy to overlook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 316313.0,
      "end_time": 318898.0,
      "text": "but that doesn&#39;t mean that they aren&#39;t important."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 318898.0,
      "end_time": 321103.0,
      "text": "A few years back, a man called Kevin Lafferty"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 321103.0,
      "end_time": 324472.0,
      "text": "took a group of scientists into three Californian estuaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 324472.0,
      "end_time": 326220.0,
      "text": "and they pretty much weighed and dissected"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 326220.0,
      "end_time": 328215.0,
      "text": "and recorded everything they could find,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 328215.0,
      "end_time": 329443.0,
      "text": "and what they found"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 329443.0,
      "end_time": 332659.0,
      "text": "were parasites in extreme abundance."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 332659.0,
      "end_time": 334703.0,
      "text": "Especially common were trematodes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 334703.0,
      "end_time": 337353.0,
      "text": "tiny worms that specialize in castrating their hosts"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 337353.0,
      "end_time": 339899.0,
      "text": "like this unfortunate snail."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 339899.0,
      "end_time": 342788.0,
      "text": "Now, a single trematode is tiny, microscopic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 342788.0,
      "end_time": 344587.0,
      "text": "but collectively they weighed as much"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 344587.0,
      "end_time": 346773.0,
      "text": "as all the fish in the estuaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 346773.0,
      "end_time": 350480.0,
      "text": "and three to nine times more than all the birds."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 350480.0,
      "end_time": 352474.0,
      "text": "And remember the Gordian worm that I showed you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 352474.0,
      "end_time": 353862.0,
      "text": "the cricket thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 353862.0,
      "end_time": 356415.0,
      "text": "One Japanese scientist called Takuya Sato"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 356415.0,
      "end_time": 358111.0,
      "text": "found that in one stream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 358111.0,
      "end_time": 360082.0,
      "text": "these things drive so many crickets"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 360082.0,
      "end_time": 361381.0,
      "text": "and grasshoppers into the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 361381.0,
      "end_time": 362690.0,
      "text": "that the drowned insects"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 362690.0,
      "end_time": 366994.0,
      "text": "make up some 60 percent of the diet of local trout."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 366994.0,
      "end_time": 369928.0,
      "text": "Manipulation is not an oddity."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 369928.0,
      "end_time": 372048.0,
      "text": "It is a critical and common part"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 372048.0,
      "end_time": 373939.0,
      "text": "of the world around us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 373939.0,
      "end_time": 375460.0,
      "text": "and scientists have now found"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 375460.0,
      "end_time": 377942.0,
      "text": "hundreds of examples of such manipulators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 377942.0,
      "end_time": 380379.0,
      "text": "and more excitingly, they&#39;re starting to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 380379.0,
      "end_time": 384437.0,
      "text": "exactly how these creatures control their hosts."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 384437.0,
      "end_time": 386961.0,
      "text": "And this is one of my favorite examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 386961.0,
      "end_time": 389418.0,
      "text": "This is Ampulex compressa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 389418.0,
      "end_time": 391642.0,
      "text": "the emerald cockroach wasp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 391642.0,
      "end_time": 393936.0,
      "text": "and it is a truth universally acknowledged"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 393936.0,
      "end_time": 395579.0,
      "text": "that an emerald cockroach wasp in possession"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 395579.0,
      "end_time": 397375.0,
      "text": "of some fertilized eggs"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 397375.0,
      "end_time": 399841.0,
      "text": "must be in want of a cockroach."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 399841.0,
      "end_time": 401041.0,
      "text": "When she finds one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 401041.0,
      "end_time": 403252.0,
      "text": "she stabs it with a stinger"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 403252.0,
      "end_time": 404701.0,
      "text": "that is also a sense organ."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 404701.0,
      "end_time": 407372.0,
      "text": "This discovery came out three weeks ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 407372.0,
      "end_time": 409677.0,
      "text": "She stabs it with a stinger that is a sense organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 409677.0,
      "end_time": 411471.0,
      "text": "equipped with small sensory bumps"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 411471.0,
      "end_time": 414026.0,
      "text": "that allow her to feel the distinctive texture"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 414026.0,
      "end_time": 416133.0,
      "text": "of a roach&#39;s brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 416133.0,
      "end_time": 419174.0,
      "text": "So like a person blindly rooting about in a bag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 419174.0,
      "end_time": 421651.0,
      "text": "she finds the brain, and she injects it with venom"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 421651.0,
      "end_time": 425852.0,
      "text": "into two very specific clusters of neurons."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 425852.0,
      "end_time": 428935.0,
      "text": "Israeli scientists Frederic Libersat and Ram Gal"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 428935.0,
      "end_time": 432660.0,
      "text": "found that the venom is a very specific chemical weapon."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 432660.0,
      "end_time": 435204.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t kill the roach, nor does it sedate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 435204.0,
      "end_time": 437331.0,
      "text": "The roach could walk away"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 437331.0,
      "end_time": 440356.0,
      "text": "or fly or run if it chose to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 440356.0,
      "end_time": 442231.0,
      "text": "but it doesn&#39;t choose to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 442231.0,
      "end_time": 445611.0,
      "text": "because the venom nixes its motivation to walk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 445611.0,
      "end_time": 446725.0,
      "text": "and only that."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 446725.0,
      "end_time": 450431.0,
      "text": "The wasp basically un-checks the escape-from-danger box"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 450431.0,
      "end_time": 452271.0,
      "text": "in the roach&#39;s operating system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 452271.0,
      "end_time": 455504.0,
      "text": "allowing her to lead her helpless victim"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 455504.0,
      "end_time": 457615.0,
      "text": "back to her lair by its antennae"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 457615.0,
      "end_time": 460254.0,
      "text": "like a person walking a dog."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 460254.0,
      "end_time": 461931.0,
      "text": "And once there, she lays an egg on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 461931.0,
      "end_time": 464207.0,
      "text": "egg hatches, devoured alive, bursts out of body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 464207.0,
      "end_time": 466396.0,
      "text": "yadda yadda yadda, you know the drill."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 466396.0,
      "end_time": 469626.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 469626.0,
      "end_time": 472506.0,
      "text": "Now I would argue that, once stung,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 472506.0,
      "end_time": 474511.0,
      "text": "the cockroach isn&#39;t a roach anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 474511.0,
      "end_time": 476861.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s more of an extension of the wasp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 476861.0,
      "end_time": 479719.0,
      "text": "just like the cricket was an extension of the Gordian worm."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 479719.0,
      "end_time": 482519.0,
      "text": "These hosts won&#39;t get to survive or reproduce."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 482519.0,
      "end_time": 484318.0,
      "text": "They have as much control over their own fates"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 484318.0,
      "end_time": 486102.0,
      "text": "as my car."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 486102.0,
      "end_time": 487602.0,
      "text": "Once the parasites get in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 487602.0,
      "end_time": 490167.0,
      "text": "the hosts don&#39;t get a say."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 490167.0,
      "end_time": 491481.0,
      "text": "Now humans, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 491481.0,
      "end_time": 493513.0,
      "text": "are no stranger to manipulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 493513.0,
      "end_time": 495873.0,
      "text": "We take drugs to shift the chemistries of our brains"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 495873.0,
      "end_time": 497004.0,
      "text": "and to change our moods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 497004.0,
      "end_time": 501024.0,
      "text": "and what are arguments or advertising or big ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 501024.0,
      "end_time": 504727.0,
      "text": "if not an attempt to influence someone else&#39;s mind?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 504727.0,
      "end_time": 506254.0,
      "text": "But our attempts at doing this"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 506254.0,
      "end_time": 508032.0,
      "text": "are crude and blundering compared"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 508032.0,
      "end_time": 511127.0,
      "text": "to the fine-grained specificity of the parasites."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 511127.0,
      "end_time": 513519.0,
      "text": "Don Draper only wishes he was as elegant"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 513519.0,
      "end_time": 518479.0,
      "text": "and precise as the emerald cockroach wasp."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 518479.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522219.00000000006,
      "text": "Now, I think this is part of what makes parasites"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 522219.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525005.0,
      "text": "so sinister and so compelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 525005.0,
      "end_time": 527627.0,
      "text": "We place such a premium on our free will"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 527627.0,
      "end_time": 528888.0,
      "text": "and our independence"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 528888.0,
      "end_time": 530469.0,
      "text": "that the prospect of losing those qualities"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 530469.0,
      "end_time": 531747.0,
      "text": "to forces unseen"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 531747.0,
      "end_time": 534915.0,
      "text": "informs many of our deepest societal fears."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 534915.0,
      "end_time": 537368.0,
      "text": "Orwellian dystopias and shadowy cabals"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 537368.0,
      "end_time": 539222.0,
      "text": "and mind-controlling supervillains --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 539222.0,
      "end_time": 542250.0,
      "text": "these are tropes that fill our darkest fiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 542250.0,
      "end_time": 547048.0,
      "text": "but in nature, they happen all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 547048.0,
      "end_time": 549680.0,
      "text": "Which leads me to an obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 549680.0,
      "end_time": 551980.0,
      "text": "and disquieting question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 551980.0,
      "end_time": 553703.0,
      "text": "Are there dark, sinister parasites"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 553703.0,
      "end_time": 555659.0,
      "text": "that are influencing our behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 555659.0,
      "end_time": 557234.0,
      "text": "without us knowing about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 557234.0,
      "end_time": 560053.0,
      "text": "besides the NSA?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 560053.0,
      "end_time": 561360.0,
      "text": "If there are any â€”"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 561360.0,
      "end_time": 565326.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 565326.0,
      "end_time": 567648.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got a red dot on my forehead now, don&#39;t I?"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 567648.0,
      "end_time": 570175.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 570175.0,
      "end_time": 573129.0,
      "text": "If there are any, this is a good candidate for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 573129.0,
      "end_time": 576407.0,
      "text": "This is Toxoplasma gondii, or Toxo, for short,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 576407.0,
      "end_time": 577996.0,
      "text": "because the terrifying creature"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 577996.0,
      "end_time": 580206.0,
      "text": "always deserves a cute nickname."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 580206.0,
      "end_time": 582488.0,
      "text": "Toxo infects mammals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 582488.0,
      "end_time": 583966.0,
      "text": "a wide variety of mammals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 583966.0,
      "end_time": 587047.0,
      "text": "but it can only sexually reproduce in a cat."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 587047.0,
      "end_time": 589808.0,
      "text": "And scientists like Joanne Webster have shown that"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 589808.0,
      "end_time": 592001.0,
      "text": "if Toxo gets into a rat or a mouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 592001.0,
      "end_time": 595473.0,
      "text": "it turns the rodent into a cat-seeking missile."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 595473.0,
      "end_time": 598549.0,
      "text": "If the infected rat smells the delightful odor"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 598549.0,
      "end_time": 599773.0,
      "text": "of cat piss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 599773.0,
      "end_time": 602493.0,
      "text": "it runs towards the source of the smell"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 602493.0,
      "end_time": 606412.0,
      "text": "rather than the more sensible direction of away."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 606412.0,
      "end_time": 608947.0,
      "text": "The cat eats the rat. Toxo gets to have sex."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 608947.0,
      "end_time": 611819.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a classic tale of Eat, Prey, Love."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 611819.0,
      "end_time": 619512.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 619512.0,
      "end_time": 622714.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re very charitable, generous people."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 622714.0,
      "end_time": 625299.0,
      "text": "Hi, Elizabeth, I loved your talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 625299.0,
      "end_time": 628667.0,
      "text": "How does the parasite control its host"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 628667.0,
      "end_time": 629871.0,
      "text": "in this way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 629871.0,
      "end_time": 631197.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t really know."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 631197.0,
      "end_time": 632885.0,
      "text": "We know that Toxo releases an enzyme"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 632885.0,
      "end_time": 634877.0,
      "text": "that makes dopamine, a substance involved"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 634877.0,
      "end_time": 636690.0,
      "text": "in reward and motivation."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 636690.0,
      "end_time": 639121.0,
      "text": "We know it targets certain parts of a rodent&#39;s brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 639121.0,
      "end_time": 641586.0,
      "text": "including those involved in sexual arousal."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 641586.0,
      "end_time": 643787.0,
      "text": "But how those puzzle pieces fit together"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 643787.0,
      "end_time": 645631.0,
      "text": "is not immediately clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 645631.0,
      "end_time": 647927.0,
      "text": "What is clear is that this thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 647927.0,
      "end_time": 649319.0,
      "text": "is a single cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 649319.0,
      "end_time": 650689.0,
      "text": "This has no nervous system."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 650689.0,
      "end_time": 651821.0,
      "text": "It has no consciousness."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 651821.0,
      "end_time": 653122.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t even have a body."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 653122.0,
      "end_time": 655746.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s manipulating a mammal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 655746.0,
      "end_time": 657172.0,
      "text": "We are mammals."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 657172.0,
      "end_time": 659606.0,
      "text": "We are more intelligent than a mere rat, to be sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 659606.0,
      "end_time": 662130.0,
      "text": "but our brains have the same basic structure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 662130.0,
      "end_time": 663523.0,
      "text": "the same types of cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 663523.0,
      "end_time": 665111.0,
      "text": "the same chemicals running through them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 665111.0,
      "end_time": 667430.0,
      "text": "and the same parasites."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 667430.0,
      "end_time": 669778.0,
      "text": "Estimates vary a lot, but some figures suggest"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 669778.0,
      "end_time": 672138.0,
      "text": "that one in three people around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 672138.0,
      "end_time": 673851.0,
      "text": "have Toxo in their brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 673851.0,
      "end_time": 677339.0,
      "text": "Now typically, this doesn&#39;t lead to any overt illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 677339.0,
      "end_time": 679217.0,
      "text": "The parasite holds up in a dormant state"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 679217.0,
      "end_time": 681400.0,
      "text": "for a long period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 681400.0,
      "end_time": 683439.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s some evidence that those people"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 683439.0,
      "end_time": 686473.0,
      "text": "who are carriers score slightly differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 686473.0,
      "end_time": 689202.0,
      "text": "on personality questionnaires than other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 689202.0,
      "end_time": 691686.0,
      "text": "that they have a slightly higher risk of car accidents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 691686.0,
      "end_time": 694289.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s some evidence that people with schizophrenia"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 694289.0,
      "end_time": 696835.0,
      "text": "are more likely to be infected."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 696835.0,
      "end_time": 699018.0,
      "text": "Now, I think this evidence is still inconclusive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 699018.0,
      "end_time": 700929.0,
      "text": "and even among Toxo researchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 700929.0,
      "end_time": 703369.0,
      "text": "opinion is divided as to whether the parasite"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 703369.0,
      "end_time": 705754.0,
      "text": "is truly influencing our behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 705754.0,
      "end_time": 708413.0,
      "text": "But given the widespread nature of such manipulations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 708413.0,
      "end_time": 710258.0,
      "text": "it would be completely implausible"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 710258.0,
      "end_time": 711907.0,
      "text": "for humans to be the only species"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 711907.0,
      "end_time": 714853.0,
      "text": "that weren&#39;t similarly affected."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 714853.0,
      "end_time": 719246.0,
      "text": "And I think that this capacity to constantly"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 719246.0,
      "end_time": 722113.0,
      "text": "subvert our way of thinking about the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 722113.0,
      "end_time": 723660.0,
      "text": "makes parasites amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 723660.0,
      "end_time": 726869.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re constantly inviting us to look at the natural world sideways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 726869.0,
      "end_time": 729040.0,
      "text": "and to ask if the behaviors we&#39;re seeing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 729040.0,
      "end_time": 730527.0,
      "text": "whether they&#39;re simple and obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 730527.0,
      "end_time": 732060.0,
      "text": "or baffling and puzzling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 732060.0,
      "end_time": 734146.0,
      "text": "are not the results of individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 734146.0,
      "end_time": 735999.0,
      "text": "acting through their own accord"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 735999.0,
      "end_time": 737808.0,
      "text": "but because they are being bent"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 737808.0,
      "end_time": 740478.0,
      "text": "to the control of something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 740478.0,
      "end_time": 742518.0,
      "text": "And while that idea may be disquieting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 742518.0,
      "end_time": 745441.0,
      "text": "and while parasites&#39; habits may be very grisly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 745441.0,
      "end_time": 747233.0,
      "text": "I think that ability to surprise us"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 747233.0,
      "end_time": 750408.0,
      "text": "makes them as wonderful and as charismatic"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 750408.0,
      "end_time": 753772.0,
      "text": "as any panda or butterfly or dolphin."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 753772.0,
      "end_time": 755991.0,
      "text": "At the end of &quot;On the Origin of Species,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 755991.0,
      "end_time": 758980.0,
      "text": "Charles Darwin writes about the grandeur of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 758980.0,
      "end_time": 761633.0,
      "text": "and of endless forms most beautiful"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 761633.0,
      "end_time": 763065.0,
      "text": "and most wonderful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 763065.0,
      "end_time": 765644.0,
      "text": "and I like to think he could easily have been talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 765644.0,
      "end_time": 768824.0,
      "text": "about a tapeworm that makes shrimp sociable"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 768824.0,
      "end_time": 772073.0,
      "text": "or a wasp that takes cockroaches for walks."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 772073.0,
      "end_time": 775222.0,
      "text": "But perhaps, that&#39;s just a parasite talking."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 775222.0,
      "end_time": 776953.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 776953.0,
      "end_time": 786953.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}